data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION WITH BOND PAID!!! If you are looking for the perfectly located home, please schedule an appointment to see this beautiful, clean, 3 bedroom 2 bath Anna Maria courtyard villa. Entering this home, you are greeted with a large, bright, open floor-plan and laminate flooring. This home is unique with a natural gas connection and comes with a gas water heater, dryer, furnace, and stove. The ROOF, HVAC System, and Water Heater have all been replaced. This home is located in the Village of Mulberry, which offers a multitude of amenities and conveniences. The NEW First Responder, Mulberry, and Chatham Recreation centers and pools are minutes away, providing fantastic opportunities for leisure and fitness activities. Medical care is nearby with the VA Clinic and medical offices only minutes away. Additionally, the Nancy Lopez and Glenview Country Clubs boast fabulous restaurants, 27-hole Championship Golf courses, tennis complexes, and aquatic centers. For sports enthusiasts, the area provides easy access to 4 executive golf courses, as well as opportunities for pickleball, tennis, platform tennis, and shuffleboard. The Villages is known for its vibrant community and a wide range of activities to suit various interests. In terms of entertainment and dining, residents will find themselves right in the heart of The Villages, with Spanish Springs and Lake Sumter Landing being two of the closest town squares. These town squares offer a diverse array of shopping options, live music and dancing venues, theaters, and a wide selection of fine restaurants. Don't miss the opportunity to see this villa today. You will be glad you did!
